our-buses-onlyfans-campaign-the-majority-of-artists-are-struggling-to-be-able-afford-to-actually-play-shows-3814791">凯特·纳什 (Kate Nash) 推出 Butts For Tour Buses OnlyFans 活动：“大多数艺术家都在努力负担得起实际演出费用”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
